{"kanda":6,"sarga":126,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"अनुज्ञातंतुरामेणतद्विमानमनुत्तमम् ।हंसयुक्तंमहानादमुत्पपातविहायसम्","trans":"Swan shaped Pushpak, unsurpassed in appearance like swan, making great sound started to fly with the permission of Rama.","words":[{"d":"अनुत्तमम्","m":"unsurpassed"},{"d":"हंसयुक्तम्","m":"like swan"},{"d":"महानादम्","m":"great sound"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"विमानम्","m":"aerial car"},{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"अनुज्ञातम्","m":"permission"},{"d":"विहायसम्","m":"started to fly"},{"d":"उत्पपात","m":"rising up"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"पातयित्वाततश्चक्षुस्सर्वतोरघुनन्दनः ।अब्रवीन्मैथिलींसीतांरामश्शशिनिभाननाम्","trans":"Then Rama, the enhancer of the joy of Raghu race casting his gaze at the moon like face of Sita spoke.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"रघुनन्दनः","m":"enhancer of joy of Raghu race"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"चक्षुः","m":"eyes"},{"d":"सर्वतः","m":"all sides"},{"d":"पातयित्वा","m":"casting"},{"d":"शशिनिभाननाम्","m":"moon like face"},{"d":"मैथिलीम्","m":"of Mythili"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"कैलासशिखराकारेत्रिकूटशिखरेस्थिताम् ।लङ्कामीक्षस्ववैदेहीनिर्मितांविश्वकर्मणा","trans":"\"Vaidehi, you may see the peak of Trikuta which stands on Lanka in the shape of the peak of Kailasa, constructed by Viswakarma.\"","words":[{"d":"वैदेहि","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"कैलासशिखराकारे","m":"of the shape of the peak of Kailasa"},{"d":"त्रिकूटशिखरे","m":"peak of Trikuta"},{"d":"स्थिताम्","m":"stands"},{"d":"विश्वकर्मणा","m":"by Viswakarma"},{"d":"निर्मिताम्","m":"constructed"},{"d":"लङ्काम्","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"ईक्षस्व","m":"you may see"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"एतदायोधनंपश्यमांसशोणितकर्दमम् ।हरीणांराक्षसानां च सीते विशसनंमहत्","trans":"\"Sita, see the mire of flesh and blood of the carnage of many monkeys and Rakshasas on the battlefield.\"","words":[{"d":"सीते","m":"Sita"},{"d":"मांसशोणितकर्दमम्","m":"mire of flesh and blood"},{"d":"हरीणाम्","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"राक्षसानां च","m":"and R